
Overview of adv unawares

The adv unawares has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (1) unawares -- (without forethought or plan; inadvertently; "came upon the diamond unawares")
2. unawares -- (suddenly and unexpectedly; "rain caught them unawares"; "sorrow comes to all, and to the young it comes with bittered agony because it takes them unawares"- A.Lincoln)
3. short, unawares -- (at a disadvantage; "I was caught short")
